Class Schedular

  • java.lang.Object
    • Schedular
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Container
    public class Schedular
extends Object
implements Container
    Schedular class implements Container interface, this class behaves like controller and has all the functions required to display job, create job or delete it from database. It iterates all the jobs in list and will produce list of jobs in app to show it to user.
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Aneel Ahmed
